data.description: This is the one you've been waiting for! All-Brick Residence Near the River! Just a mile from the scenic river and boat ramp lies this expansive 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom home combining durability and classic aesthetics. With features such as a wood-burning fireplace in the expansive living room, a modern well pump installed just 5 years ago, and a wealth of cabinet space in the kitchen, every detail has been considered. The property further boasts large spare bedrooms, a spacious laundry room, two attics for ample storage, and a versatile flex space adaptable to your needs. Outside, find a powered shed perfect for additional storage or hobbies. Experience the blend of serenity and function this home offers, all while being moments away from the beauty of riverside living.
